h3#sources Which are the sources?
p
	| You only got to add the CSS, JavaScript and assets of Chico UI, and that's all!
form.container(action="/download")
	input.ch-btn.ch-primary#download(type="submit", value="Download v#{latest.version}")
p
	| Make sure to add the stylesheet call into the 
	code &lt;head&gt;
	|  tag.
pre
	| <link rel="stylesheet" href="chico-min-x.x.x.css" />
p
	| And you should add the JavaScript at bottom of page, before 
	code &lt;/body&gt;
	|  tag close and 
	strong after jQuery script call
	| .
pre
	| <script src="build/chico-min-x.x.x.js"></script>
p
	| Assets (images and icons) are into the 
	strong zip file
	|  that you 
	a(href="/download") download
	| . Put assets on a folder into your project and link to files within stylesheet code.

